this whole time?

1:27:20.806 --> 1:27:22.311
No, Fletch.

1:27:22.346 --> 1:27:25.908
It's just that I fall in love
with idiots.

1:27:25.943 --> 1:27:28.812
I may be an idiot,
but I saved your life.

1:27:29.485 --> 1:27:31.045
You didn't.

1:27:31.080 --> 1:27:33.487
That girl,
she saved both of our lives.

1:27:33.522 --> 1:27:34.950
Well--
