1:27:40.254 --> 1:27:41.627
Hold on one second.

1:27:44.929 --> 1:27:46.731
Oh, this is fun song.

1:27:47.327 --> 1:27:49.063
Griz, one last thing.

1:27:49.098 --> 1:27:52.000
