splendidly.

1:29:06.175 --> 1:29:08.076
Hmm.

1:29:08.111 --> 1:29:11.981
Well, it turns out...
...the Countess
actually loves you.

1:29:12.016 --> 1:29:13.884
She was even able
to forgive Angela.

1:29:13.919 --> 1:29:16.458
-She's a remarkable woman.
-That she is.

1:29:16.493 --> 1:29:19.659
And in Angela's defense,
she didn't know
about the murder.

1:29:19.694 --> 1:29:22.794
I think she stole the paintings
